text: Hey @FedEx you are really making my life hard. Package was supposed to be delivered today. Driver did not knock and just left a door tag. We called they assured redeliver today and then did not even try. Now they tell me I have to wait until Monday. That package has my pay check

@StillWithTrump Hi, this is Lakin. I do apologize for the delay in response. We are currently experiencing high volumes of social inquiries. I'd be happy to research this issue. Please DM your name, address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, and phone number. https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r
@FedExHelp issue resolved after hours on the phone. FedEx is not the company it once was. You need to bring your telephone support back to the United States!
@StillWithTrump I am glad the issue has been resolved. -Lakin
